<td><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://cityofromney.com/">City of Romney</a></td>
</tr>
</table>
<p><b>Romney</b> is a city in and the <a href="/wiki/County_seat" title="County seat">county seat</a> of <a href="/wiki/Hampshire_County,_West_Virginia" title="Hampshire County, West Virginia">Hampshire County</a>, <a href="/wiki/West_Virginia" title="West Virginia">West Virginia</a>, USA.<sup id="cite_ref-GR6_5-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-GR6-5">[5]</a></sup> The population was 1,940 at the <a href="/wiki/2000_United_States_Census" title="2000 United States Census">2000 census</a>, while the <a href="/wiki/ZIP_Code_Tabulation_Area" title="ZIP Code Tabulation Area">area covered</a> by the city's <a href="/wiki/ZIP_code" class="mw-redirect" title="ZIP code">ZIP code</a> had a population of 5,873. The population was 1,848 at the <a href="/wiki/2010_United_States_Census" title="2010 United States Census">2010 census</a>.</p>
<p></p>
